Question: Can you tell me which faculty did the most research projects? I just need their name (nama) and the number of projects (total_proyek).
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT f.nama, COUNT(pp.id_proyek) AS total_proyek
FROM Fakultas f
JOIN ProyekPenelitian pp ON f.id_fakultas = pp.id_fakultas
GROUP BY f.id_fakultas, f.nama
ORDER BY total_proyek DESC
LIMIT 1;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT f.nama, COUNT(p.id_proyek) AS total_proyek
  FROM Fakultas f
  JOIN ProyekPenelitian p ON f.id_fakultas = p.id_fakultas
  GROUP BY f.nama
  ORDER BY total_proyek DESC
  LIMIT 1;

Question: I’m curious which lecturer guides the most students. Please show their name (nama) and how many students they supervise (total_mahasiswa_dibimbing).

  LIMIT 1;

Question: Which student joined the most sessions? I want to see their name (nama) and how many sessions they attended (total_kehadiran).

GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama

LIMIT 1;

  FROM Mahasiswa m
  JOIN CatatanKehadiran k ON m.id_mahasiswa = k.id_mahasiswa
  GROUP BY m.nama
  ORDER BY total_kehadiran DESC
  LIMIT 1;

Question: What are the top 5 most popular courses? Show me the course title (judul) and how many students joined (total_mahasiswa).
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT mk.judul, COUNT(DISTINCT ek.id_mahasiswa) AS total_mahasiswa
FROM MataKuliah mk
LEFT JOIN Sesi s ON mk.id_mk = s.id_mk
LEFT JOIN EnrolmenKelas ek ON s.id_sesi = ek.id_sesi
GROUP BY mk.judul
ORDER BY total_mahasiswa DESC
LIMIT 5;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT mk.judul, COUNT(e.id_mahasiswa) AS total_mahasiswa
  FROM MataKuliah mk
  JOIN Sesi s ON mk.id_mk = s.id_mk
  JOIN EnrolmenKelas e ON s.id_sesi = e.id_sesi
  GROUP BY mk.judul
  ORDER BY total_mahasiswa DESC
  LIMIT 5;

Question: Which course has the best average exam score? Show me the title (judul) and the average score (rata_rata_nilai).
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT mk.judul, AVG(hu.nilai_diperoleh) AS rata_rata_nilai
FROM MataKuliah mk
JOIN Ujian u ON mk.id_mk = u.id_mk
JOIN HasilUjian hu ON u.id_ujian = hu.id_ujian
GROUP BY mk.id_mk, mk.judul
ORDER BY rata_rata_nilai DESC
LIMIT 1;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT mk.judul, AVG(h.nilai_diperoleh) AS rata_rata_nilai
  FROM MataKuliah mk
  JOIN Ujian u ON mk.id_mk = u.id_mk
  JOIN HasilUjian h ON u.id_ujian = h.id_ujian
  GROUP BY mk.judul
  ORDER BY rata_rata_nilai DESC
  LIMIT 1;

LIMIT 1;

Question: Can you list all faculties and show how many research projects, publications, and active lecturers each has? Show nama, total_proyek, total_publikasi, total_dosen_aktif.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    f.nama,
    COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) AS total_proyek,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.id_publikasi) AS total_publikasi,
    COUNT(DISTINCT d.id_dosen) AS total_dosen_aktif
FROM 
    Fakultas f
LEFT JOIN 
    ProyekPenelitian pp ON f.id_fakultas = pp.id_fakultas
LEFT JOIN 
    Publikasi p ON f.id_fakultas = p.id_fakultas
LEFT JOIN 
    Dosen d ON f.id_fakultas = d.id_fakultas
GROUP BY 
    f.id_fakultas, f.nama
ORDER BY 
    f.id_fakultas;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT f.nama,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.id_proyek) AS total_proyek,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pb.id_publikasi) AS total_publikasi,
  COUNT(DISTINCT d.id_dosen) AS total_dosen_aktif
  FROM Fakultas f
  LEFT JOIN ProyekPenelitian p ON f.id_fakultas = p.id_fakultas
  LEFT JOIN Publikasi pb ON f.id_fakultas = pb.id_fakultas
  LEFT JOIN Dosen d ON d.id_fakultas = f.id_fakultas
  WHERE d.id_dosen IN (
  SELECT id_dosen FROM PenulisPublikasi
  UNION
  SELECT id_dosen FROM ProyekPenelitian
  )
  GROUP BY f.nama;

Question: Which students joined more than 2 projects and are in a club? Show id_mahasiswa, nama, total_proyek, and total_klub.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    m.id_mahasiswa, 
    m.nama, 
    COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) AS total_proyek, 
    COUNT(DISTINCT kk.id_klub) AS total_klub
FROM 
    Mahasiswa m
JOIN 
    PartisipasiPenelitian pp ON m.id_mahasiswa = pp.id_mahasiswa
JOIN 
    KeanggotaanKlub kk ON m.id_mahasiswa = kk.id_mahasiswa
GROUP BY 
    m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) > 2;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) AS total_proyek,
  COUNT(DISTINCT kk.id_klub) AS total_klub
  FROM Mahasiswa m
  JOIN PartisipasiPenelitian pp ON m.id_mahasiswa = pp.id_mahasiswa
  JOIN KeanggotaanKlub kk ON m.id_mahasiswa = kk.id_mahasiswa
  GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) > 2;

Question: List all courses with both a session and an exam, and show the average grade and exam score. Show id_mk, judul, avg_nilai_akhir, avg_nilai_ujian.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    mk.id_mk,
    mk.judul,
    AVG(n.nilai_akhir) AS avg_nilai_akhir,
    AVG(hu.nilai_diperoleh) AS avg_nilai_ujian
FROM 
    MataKuliah mk
JOIN 
    Nilai n ON mk.id_mk = n.id_mk
JOIN 
    Ujian u ON mk.id_mk = u.id_mk
JOIN 
    HasilUjian hu ON u.id_ujian = hu.id_ujian
JOIN 
    Sesi s ON mk.id_mk = s.id_mk
GROUP BY 
    mk.id_mk, mk.judul
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.id_sesi) > 0 AND COUNT(DISTINCT u.id_ujian) > 0;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT mk.id_mk, mk.judul,
  AVG(n.nilai_akhir) AS avg_nilai_akhir,
  AVG(h.nilai_diperoleh) AS avg_nilai_ujian
  FROM MataKuliah mk
  JOIN Nilai n ON mk.id_mk = n.id_mk
  JOIN Ujian u ON mk.id_mk = u.id_mk
  JOIN HasilUjian h ON u.id_ujian = h.id_ujian AND n.id_mahasiswa = h.id_mahasiswa
  GROUP BY mk.id_mk, mk.judul
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT u.id_ujian) > 0;

Question: Which faculties have clubs joined by students from different majors? I want id_fakultas, nama, and total_jurusan_klub.

Question: List students who got a grade for every course they attended. Show id_mahasiswa, nama, and jumlah_mk.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    m.id_mahasiswa, 
    m.nama, 
    COUNT(DISTINCT k.id_mk) AS jumlah_mk
FROM 
    Mahasiswa m
JOIN 
    Kelas k ON m.id_mahasiswa = k.id_mahasiswa
WHERE 
    NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT k2.id_mk
        FROM Kelas k2
        WHERE k2.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
        EXCEPT
        SELECT n.id_mk
        FROM Nilai n
        WHERE n.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
    )
GROUP BY 
    m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama, COUNT(DISTINCT n.id_mk) AS jumlah_mk
  FROM Mahasiswa m
  JOIN Nilai n ON m.id_mahasiswa = n.id_mahasiswa
  JOIN EnrolmenKelas e ON m.id_mahasiswa = e.id_mahasiswa
  JOIN Sesi s ON e.id_sesi = s.id_sesi
  GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT n.id_mk) = (
  SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s2.id_mk)
  FROM EnrolmenKelas e2
  JOIN Sesi s2 ON s2.id_sesi = e2.id_sesi
  WHERE e2.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
  );

Question: Which student is most active overall (sessions, research, clubs)? Show id_mahasiswa, nama, total_sesi, total_proyek, total_klub.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    m.id_mahasiswa,
    m.nama,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ek.id_sesi) AS total_sesi,
    COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) AS total_proyek,
    COUNT(DISTINCT kk.id_klub) AS total_klub,
    (COUNT(DISTINCT ek.id_sesi) + (COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) * 2 + (COUNT(DISTINCT kk.id_klub) * 1.5) AS skor_aktivitas
FROM 
    Mahasiswa m
LEFT JOIN 
    EnrolmenKelas ek ON m.id_mahasiswa = ek.id_mahasiswa
LEFT JOIN 
    PartisipasiPenelitian pp ON m.id_mahasiswa = pp.id_mahasiswa
LEFT JOIN 
    KeanggotaanKlub kk ON m.id_mahasiswa = kk.id_mahasiswa
GROUP BY 
    m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama
ORDER BY 
    skor_aktivitas DESC
LIMIT 1;

  COUNT(DISTINCT k.id_sesi) AS total_sesi,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) AS total_proyek,
  COUNT(DISTINCT kk.id_klub) AS total_klub
FROM Mahasiswa m

LEFT JOIN PartisipasiPenelitian pp ON pp.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa

GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama

Question: Mahasiswa mana yang paling aktif secara akademik? Kolom: id_mahasiswa, nama, total_sesi, total_proyek, total_klub.
Generated SQL Query:
WITH SesiMahasiswa AS (
    SELECT id_mahasiswa, COUNT(DISTINCT id_sesi) AS total_sesi
    FROM EnrolmenKelas
    GROUP BY id_mahasiswa
),
ProyekMahasiswa AS (
    SELECT id_mahasiswa, COUNT(DISTINCT id_proyek) AS total_proyek
    FROM PartisipasiPenelitian
    GROUP BY id_mahasiswa
),
KlubMahasiswa AS (
    SELECT id_mahasiswa, COUNT(DISTINCT id_klub) AS total_klub
    FROM KeanggotaanKlub
    GROUP BY id_mahasiswa
),
TotalAktivitas AS (
    SELECT 
        m.id_mahasiswa,
        m.nama,
        COALESCE(s.total_sesi, 0) AS total_sesi,
        COALESCE(p.total_proyek, 0) AS total_proyek,
        COALESCE(k.total_klub, 0) AS total_klub,
        (COALESCE(s.total_sesi, 0) + COALESCE(p.total_proyek, 0) + COALESCE(k.total_klub, 0)) AS total_aktivitas
    FROM Mahasiswa m
    LEFT JOIN SesiMahasiswa s ON m.id_mahasiswa = s.id_mahasiswa
    LEFT JOIN ProyekMahasiswa p ON m.id_mahasiswa = p.id_mahasiswa
    LEFT JOIN KlubMahasiswa k ON m.id_mahasiswa = k.id_mahasiswa
)
SELECT id_mahasiswa, nama, total_sesi, total_proyek, total_klub
FROM TotalAktivitas
WHERE total_aktivitas = (SELECT MAX(total_aktivitas) FROM TotalAktivitas);
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama,
  COUNT(DISTINCT k.id_sesi) AS total_sesi,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) AS total_proyek,
  COUNT(DISTINCT kk.id_klub) AS total_klub
FROM Mahasiswa m
LEFT JOIN CatatanKehadiran k ON k.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
LEFT JOIN PartisipasiPenelitian pp ON pp.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
LEFT JOIN KeanggotaanKlub kk ON kk.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama
ORDER BY (COUNT(DISTINCT k.id_sesi) + COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_proyek) + COUNT(DISTINCT kk.id_klub)) DESC
LIMIT 1;

Question: Which students have top GPA and their advisor published something? Show id_mahasiswa, nama, IPK, total_publikasi_pembimbing.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    m.id_mahasiswa,
    m.nama,
    n.IPK,
    COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_publikasi) AS total_publikasi_pembimbing
FROM 
    Mahasiswa m
JOIN 
    Nilai n ON m.id_mahasiswa = n.id_mahasiswa
JOIN 
    Dosen d ON m.id_pembimbing = d.id_dosen
JOIN 
    PenulisPublikasi pp ON d.id_dosen = pp.id_dosen
WHERE 
    n.IPK = (SELECT MAX(IPK) FROM Nilai)
GROUP BY 
    m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama, n.IPK;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama, MAX(n.IPK) AS IPK,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_publikasi) AS total_publikasi_pembimbing
  FROM Mahasiswa m
  JOIN Nilai n ON n.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
  JOIN Dosen d ON d.id_dosen = m.id_pembimbing
  JOIN PenulisPublikasi pp ON pp.id_dosen = d.id_dosen
  WHERE n.IPK > (SELECT percentile_cont(0.9) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY IPK) FROM Nilai)
  GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama;

Question: Siapa mahasiswa IPK-nya masuk top 10% dan pembimbingnya pernah publikasi? Kolom: id_mahasiswa, nama, IPK, total_publikasi_pembimbing.
Generated SQL Query:
WITH TopStudents AS (
    SELECT 
        m.id_mahasiswa,
        m.nama,
        n.IPK,
        m.id_pembimbing
    FROM 
        Mahasiswa m
    JOIN 
        Nilai n ON m.id_mahasiswa = n.id_mahasiswa
    ORDER BY 
        n.IPK DESC
    LIMIT (SELECT CEIL(COUNT(*) * 0.1) FROM Mahasiswa)
),
AdvisorPublications AS (
    SELECT 
        d.id_dosen,
        COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_publikasi) AS total_publikasi_pembimbing
    FROM 
        Dosen d
    JOIN 
        PenulisPublikasi pp ON d.id_dosen = pp.id_dosen
    GROUP BY 
        d.id_dosen
)

SELECT 
    ts.id_mahasiswa,
    ts.nama,
    ts.IPK,
    COALESCE(ap.total_publikasi_pembimbing, 0) AS total_publikasi_pembimbing
FROM 
    TopStudents ts
LEFT JOIN 
    AdvisorPublications ap ON ts.id_pembimbing = ap.id_dosen
ORDER BY 
    ts.IPK DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama, MAX(n.IPK) AS IPK,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pp.id_publikasi) AS total_publikasi_pembimbing
  FROM Mahasiswa m
  JOIN Nilai n ON n.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
  JOIN Dosen d ON d.id_dosen = m.id_pembimbing
  JOIN PenulisPublikasi pp ON pp.id_dosen = d.id_dosen
  WHERE n.IPK > (SELECT percentile_cont(0.9) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY IPK) FROM Nilai)
  GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama;

Question: Which faculties have a head who doesn’t teach? Show id_fakultas, nama, id_kepala, nama_kepala.

LEFT JOIN MataKuliah mk ON d.id_dosen = mk.id_pengajar

WHERE mk.id_pengajar IS NULL AND s.id_pengajar IS NULL;

Question: Fakultas mana yang kepala fakultasnya ga pernah ngajar? Kolom: id_fakultas, nama, id_kepala, nama_kepala.

FROM Fakultas f
JOIN Dosen d ON f.id_kepala = d.id_dosen
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM MataKuliah mk
    WHERE mk.id_pengajar = f.id_kepala
) AND NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM Sesi s
    WHERE s.id_pengajar = f.id_kepala
);

Question: Who got the highest score in each exam? Show id_ujian, id_mahasiswa, nama, nilai_diperoleh.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    u.id_ujian,
    h.id_mahasiswa,
    m.nama,
    h.nilai_diperoleh
FROM 
    Ujian u
JOIN 
    HasilUjian h ON u.id_ujian = h.id_ujian
JOIN 
    Mahasiswa m ON h.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
WHERE 
    (u.id_ujian, h.nilai_diperoleh) IN (
        SELECT 
            id_ujian, 
            MAX(nilai_diperoleh) 
        FROM 
            HasilUjian 
        GROUP BY 
            id_ujian
    )
ORDER BY 
    u.id_ujian;
Expected SQL Query:

  FROM HasilUjian h
  JOIN Mahasiswa m ON m.id_mahasiswa = h.id_mahasiswa
  WHERE h.nilai_diperoleh = (
  SELECT MAX(h2.nilai_diperoleh)
  FROM HasilUjian h2
  WHERE h2.id_ujian = h.id_ujian
  );

Question: Siapa aja mahasiswa dengan nilai tertinggi di setiap ujian? Kolom: id_ujian, id_mahasiswa, nama, nilai_diperoleh.

    SELECT

        MAX(nilai_diperoleh) AS max_nilai
    FROM HasilUjian

    hu.id_ujian,
    m.id_mahasiswa,
    m.nama,
    hu.nilai_diperoleh
FROM Mahasiswa m
JOIN HasilUjian hu ON m.id_mahasiswa = hu.id_mahasiswa
JOIN MaxScores ms ON hu.id_ujian = ms.id_ujian AND hu.nilai_diperoleh = ms.max_nilai
ORDER BY hu.id_ujian;

  WHERE h2.id_ujian = h.id_ujian
  );

Question: Which books were never borrowed but are in a category that others borrow often? Show id_buku, judul, kategori.
Generated SQL Query:
WITH frequently_borrowed_categories AS (
    SELECT kategori, COUNT(*) AS borrow_count
    FROM PeminjamanBuku pb
    JOIN BukuPerpustakaan bp ON pb.id_buku = bp.id_buku
    GROUP BY kategori
    ORDER BY borrow_count DESC
    LIMIT 5
),
never_borrowed_books AS (
    SELECT bp.id_buku, bp.judul, bp.kategori
    FROM BukuPerpustakaan bp
    LEFT JOIN PeminjamanBuku pb ON bp.id_buku = pb.id_buku
    WHERE pb.id_peminjaman IS NULL
)
SELECT nbb.id_buku, nbb.judul, nbb.kategori
FROM never_borrowed_books nbb
JOIN frequently_borrowed_categories fbc ON nbb.kategori = fbc.kategori;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT b.id_buku, b.judul, b.kategori
  FROM BukuPerpustakaan b
  WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM PeminjamanBuku p WHERE p.id_buku = b.id_buku
  )
  AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM BukuPerpustakaan b2
  JOIN PeminjamanBuku p2 ON p2.id_buku = b2.id_buku
  WHERE b2.kategori = b.kategori
  GROUP BY b2.kategori
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 3
  );

  JOIN PenulisPublikasi pp ON pp.id_dosen = d.id_dosen
  GROUP BY m.id_mahasiswa, m.nama, d.id_dosen, d.nama;

Question: Mahasiswa mana yang dosennya juga nulis publikasi? Kolom: id_mahasiswa, nama, id_pembimbing, nama_dosen, total_publikasi.

Question: Which lecturers teach and lead research but don’t supervise students? Show id_dosen, nama.
Dosen mana yang ngajar dan riset tapi ga bimbing mahasiswa? Kolom: id_dosen, nama.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT d.id_dosen, d.nama 
FROM Dosen d 
JOIN (
    (SELECT DISTINCT id_pengajar AS id_dosen FROM MataKuliah 
     INTERSECT 
     SELECT DISTINCT id_dosen FROM ProyekPenelitian) 
    EXCEPT 
    SELECT DISTINCT id_pembimbing AS id_dosen FROM Mahasiswa
) t ON d.id_dosen = t.id_dosen

Question: Which facilities are accessed by all faculties? Show id_fasilitas, nama.
Generated SQL Query:

FROM Fasilitas f
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM Fakultas fa
    WHERE NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM FasilitasFakultas ff
        WHERE ff.id_fasilitas = f.id_fasilitas
        AND ff.id_fakultas = fa.id_fakultas
    )
);

SELECT f.id_fasilitas, f.nama
  FROM Fasilitas f

  SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ff.id_fakultas)
  FROM FasilitasFakultas ff
  WHERE ff.id_fasilitas = f.id_fasilitas
  ) = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Fakultas);

Question: Which departments have students with above-average GPA? Show id_jurusan, nama_jurusan, jumlah_mahasiswa_unggul.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    j.id_jurusan, 
    j.nama AS nama_jurusan, 
    COUNT(DISTINCT m.id_mahasiswa) AS jumlah_mahasiswa_unggul
FROM 
    Jurusan j
JOIN 
    Mahasiswa m ON j.id_jurusan = m.id_jurusan
JOIN 
    Nilai n ON m.id_mahasiswa = n.id_mahasiswa
WHERE 
    n.IPK > (SELECT AVG(IPK) FROM Nilai)
GROUP BY 
    j.id_jurusan, j.nama
ORDER BY 
    jumlah_mahasiswa_unggul DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT 
  j.id_jurusan, 
  j.nama AS nama_jurusan, 
  COUNT(CASE WHEN n.IPK > sub.rata2 THEN 1 END) AS jumlah_mahasiswa_unggul
FROM Jurusan j
LEFT JOIN Mahasiswa m ON m.id_jurusan = j.id_jurusan
LEFT JOIN (
  SELECT 
    m.id_jurusan, 
    AVG(n.IPK) AS rata2
  FROM Mahasiswa m
  JOIN Nilai n ON n.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
  GROUP BY m.id_jurusan
) sub ON j.id_jurusan = sub.id_jurusan
LEFT JOIN Nilai n ON n.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
GROUP BY j.id_jurusan, j.nama;

Question: Which clubs have only students from the same department? Show id_klub, nama_klub, id_jurusan.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT ok.id_klub, ok.nama AS nama_klub, j.id_jurusan
FROM OrganisasiKlub ok
JOIN KeanggotaanKlub kk ON ok.id_klub = kk.id_klub
JOIN Mahasiswa m ON kk.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
JOIN Jurusan j ON m.id_jurusan = j.id_jurusan
GROUP BY ok.id_klub, ok.nama, j.id_jurusan
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT m.id_jurusan) = 1;

  FROM OrganisasiKlub k
  JOIN KeanggotaanKlub kk ON kk.id_klub = k.id_klub
  JOIN Mahasiswa m ON kk.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
  GROUP BY k.id_klub, k.nama, m.id_jurusan
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT m.id_jurusan) = 1;

Question: Klub mana yang semua anggotanya dari satu jurusan aja? Kolom: id_klub, nama_klub, id_jurusan.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    ok.id_klub,
    ok.nama AS nama_klub,
    MIN(m.id_jurusan) AS id_jurusan
FROM 
    OrganisasiKlub ok
JOIN 
    KeanggotaanKlub kk ON ok.id_klub = kk.id_klub
JOIN 
    Mahasiswa m ON kk.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
GROUP BY 
    ok.id_klub, ok.nama
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT m.id_jurusan) = 1;

  FROM OrganisasiKlub k
  JOIN KeanggotaanKlub kk ON kk.id_klub = k.id_klub
  JOIN Mahasiswa m ON kk.id_mahasiswa = m.id_mahasiswa
